{
  "stem": "11000.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember my dad had a friend who went to one of his campaign speeches, to Hitler's campaign speeches.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember when he came back he told my mother, he said, you know, my friend told me this man is very dangerous.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, when he stood there and listened to him screaming and yelling, and he said this lady that stood next to him said to him, look at this man.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Doesn't he remind you of God?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And life started to change rapidly after he became the head of the country.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Linnich itself, we had-- Jewish life was great.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had no problems.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had friends.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My friends were non-Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My parents socialized with non-Jewish friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The word Jew never was a question.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The only difference was on Sundays, they went to their church.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And on Saturdays, we went to our temple.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had a great community life there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had a rabbi, who was also the teacher.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had our own school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there were only about 15, 18 Jewish families in the whole town.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Remarkable thing was, they all had a business.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Looking back, I don't think anybody had a job.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Everybody had a little business somehow, whether it was the tailor or the shoemaker.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I would say, all in all, it was a good life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We had a kosher butcher store.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And our rabbi's name was Max Gottlieb.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He was a man out in the community, very well-respected.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Like I said, until gradually, the change came.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And sure enough, we noticed people who became members of the Nazi party.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they formed their groups.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I remember when they first started marching and singing songs, anti-Semitic songs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I remember when they passed our house in groups and marched.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
